{"tid":1584403,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個被捕師，咁既行程真係得啖笑","createTime":"2019-09-21T05:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T06:04:21.000Z","uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c798f19f41eeed74ea130c8124511f470b56c924","tid":1584403,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:54:17.000Z","msg":"講真咁同直接宣佈黃之鋒入臭格有咩分別。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n令我地班黃絲帶 totally no mood to 捱夜嗌放人 嗱,我又分析下 首先機場特警,唔好玩啦 popo 野，6分穩陣<br />\r\n<br />\r\n警犬,,如果係真警犬就有可觀性(順便可以報上次ga仇)(不過算啦,入到臭格又會見到面) 我真係冇睇過依隊野..半力夠WIN,又6分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n最後一隊,我連名都唔記得 我地搵政黨幫黃之鋒手is ok,又6分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n加上我地4大尖刀 黃之鋒,黃台仰,方東昇, 加上關鍵王梁天琦.. 根本場場大炒,,,,<br />\r\n<br />\r\n18分就一定..係睇下破唔破到得失球.咁一面倒ga比賽,我冇興趣,大家16強見<br />\r\n<br />\r\nP.S.比d咁ga對手魚拉突..is侮辱..哈"},{"pid":"947e0b8887fdaa21156bbb7495a866d201a42b9e","tid":1584403,"uid":38189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:56:10.000Z","msg":"樓主係被捕師 咁父哥係咩師"},{"pid":"8e2a3428bb0562f9da0490decb06a97d51e64004","tid":1584403,"uid":124020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:56:33.000Z","msg":"咪得罪獌狗啊<br />\n佢地好能惡架<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係人版<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee0ba15c4eed278b411343dedb5540d222b1fa3","tid":1584403,"uid":95571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:56:51.000Z","msg":"👍👍👍👍🤘"},{"pid":"a63e1d681ddbc2c1c6de8a0e312f462da35f4bb3","tid":1584403,"uid":4206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"947e0b8887fdaa21156bbb7495a866d201a42b9e","tid":1584403,"uid":38189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:56:10.000Z","msg":"樓主係被捕師 咁父哥係咩師"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:57:02.000Z","msg":"_人師"},{"pid":"d7db30c21d41db0eb77b61dd22227ca347ec9c79","tid":1584403,"uid":52571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8e2a3428bb0562f9da0490decb06a97d51e64004","tid":1584403,"uid":124020,"